*Czech: [[zámek]]  ''m'' (1) [[zdymadlo]] ''n'', [[plavební komora]] ''f''  (2), [[lokna]] ''f'' (3)
*Dutch: [[slot]] ''n'' (1), [[sluis]] ''f'' (2), [[lok]] ''f'' (3), [[haan]] ''m'' (4)
*Finnish: [[lukko]] (1, 4), [[sulku]] (2), [[kihara]] (3)
